@startuml
title ResearchHub Deployment Sequence Diagram

actor Developer
participant "Git Repository" as Git
participant "Jenkins CI/CD" as Jenkins
participant "Terraform" as TF
participant "AWS S3" as S3
participant "AWS CloudFront" as CF
participant "AWS ECR" as ECR
participant "AWS ECS" as ECS
participant "AWS Lambda" as Lambda
participant "AWS Elasticsearch" as ES
participant "Contentful CMS" as Contentful

== Code Push and CI/CD Trigger ==
Developer -> Git: Push code to branch\n(sandbox/dev/test/prod)
Git -> Jenkins: Trigger pipeline based on branch

== Infrastructure Deployment ==
Jenkins -> TF: Execute Terraform plan
TF -> TF: Load environment-specific\ntfvars file
TF -> S3: Create/Update S3 buckets
TF -> CF: Create/Update CloudFront distributions
TF -> ECR: Create/Update ECR repositories
TF -> ECS: Create/Update ECS clusters
TF -> ES: Create/Update Elasticsearch instance
TF -> Lambda: Create/Update Lambda functions
TF -> Jenkins: Infrastructure deployment complete

== Frontend Deployment (research-hub-web) ==
Jenkins -> Jenkins: Build Angular application
Jenkins -> Jenkins: Run tests (Cypress E2E)
Jenkins -> S3: Upload static assets\n(HTML, CSS, JS)
S3 -> CF: Invalidate CloudFront cache
CF -> Jenkins: Frontend deployment complete

== GraphQL API Deployment (cer-graphql) ==
Jenkins -> Jenkins: Build Docker image\nfor GraphQL server
Jenkins -> ECR: Push Docker image
ECR -> Jenkins: Image push complete
Jenkins -> ECS: Update ECS service\nwith new image
ECS -> ECR: Pull latest image
ECS -> ECS: Deploy container\n(Apollo GraphQL server)
ECS -> Contentful: Establish connection\nfor schema proxy
ECS -> Jenkins: GraphQL API deployment complete

== Search Proxy Deployment (hub-search-proxy) ==
Jenkins -> Jenkins: Package Lambda function\n(Serverless Framework)
Jenkins -> Lambda: Deploy serverless.yml\nand handler.js
Lambda -> ES: Configure connection\nto Elasticsearch
Lambda -> Jenkins: Search proxy deployment complete

== Post-Deployment Configuration ==
Jenkins -> Lambda: Trigger bulk upload\n(Cron/HTTP event)
Lambda -> Contentful: Fetch all content
Contentful -> Lambda: Return content data
Lambda -> ES: Bulk index content
ES -> Lambda: Indexing complete
Lambda -> Jenkins: Search index initialized

== Verification ==
Jenkins -> CF: Health check frontend
CF -> Jenkins: Frontend healthy
Jenkins -> ECS: Health check GraphQL API
ECS -> Jenkins: API healthy
Jenkins -> Lambda: Test search functionality
Lambda -> Jenkins: Search operational
Jenkins -> Developer: Deployment successful

@enduml
